Block matrices
The joint mean 
  
    
      
        
          μ
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbf {\mu } }
   and joint covariance matrix 
  
    
      
        
          Σ
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbf {\Sigma } }
   of 
  
    
      
        
