    {\displaystyle \operatorname {K} _{\mathbf {Y|X} }=\operatorname {K} _{\mathbf {YY} }-\operatorname {K} _{\mathbf {YX} }\operatorname {K} _{\mathbf {XX} }^{-1}\operatorname {K} _{\mathbf {XY} }.}
  The matrix 
  
    
      
        
          K
          
            
              Y
              X
            
          
        
        ⁡
        
          K
          
            
              X
              X
            
          
          
            −
            1
          
        
      
    
