   is known as the matrix of regression coefficients, while in linear algebra 
  
    
      
        
          K
          
            
              Y
              
                |
              
              X
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \operatorname {K} _{\mathbf {Y|X} }}
   is the Schur complement of 
  
    
      
        
          K
          
            
              X
              X
            
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \operatorname {K} _{\mathbf {XX} }}
