    {\displaystyle \langle \mathbf {X} \rangle ={\frac {1}{n}}\sum _{j=1}^{n}\mathbf {X} _{j}}
  and the covariance matrix is estimated by the sample covariance matrix

  
    
      
        cov
        ⁡
        (
        
          X
        
        ,
        
          Y
        
        )
        ≈
        ⟨
        
          X
          
            Y
            
              
                T
              
            
          
        
